    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone comfortable with a few imperfections. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches and minor dings on the exterior body panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, and the air conditioning takes a moment to reach full cooling capacity. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely require some suspension work and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done but is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
      "price": 21500.0,
