    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to a standard that rivals its original showroom delivery. This vehicle exhibits an unblemished aesthetic and absolute mechanical integrity, reflecting a legacy of meticulous, climate-controlled preservation. From the pristine upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, every detail confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defines the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 43900.0,
