    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s a total dream car and has been pampered since day one\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly flawless condition, inside and out, and drives like a cloud. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to fall in love the moment you see it. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
