    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is flawless, featuring its original high-gloss factory paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is in showroom condition, retaining that new-car scent with leather upholstery that remains supple and completely free of creases or wear. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and pristine, supported by a complete, chronological service history binder. It has never seen salt or inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a 'time capsule' vehicle that performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 43500.0,
