    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so incredibly excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such breathtaking shape\u2014it really feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor. I have babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. You\u2019ve seriously gotta see it in person to believe how pristine it is! I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so come grab this beauty while it's still available!",
